@startuml
title Builder - Ejemplo 1 - Implementacion Generica
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  interface Builder <<interfaz>> {
  }
  class ConcreteBuilder {
    +buildHeader(): void
    +buildBody(): void
    +buildFooter(): void
    +result(): Product
  }
  class Director {
    +construct(Builder builder): Product
  }
  class Product {
    +setHeader(String header): void
    +setBody(String body): void
    +setFooter(String footer): void
    +toString(): String
  }
}

Builder <|.. ConcreteBuilder
Builder ..> Product : crea
ConcreteBuilder ..> Product : crea
Main ..> ConcreteBuilder : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
